data.description: Beautiful 3 BR, 2 BA*** sought-after lake community, Lake Wilderness.  The spacious Living Room is accented with a cozy gas fireplace. The Kitchen is sun-kissed through a skylight and offers a Pantry too. The Laundry Room is located just off of the Kitchen and includes the Washer and Dryer. The split Bedroom design gives plenty of privacy for all. The Primary Bedroom includes Primary Bath with a skylight, soaker tub, and walk-in closet. The gorgeous fenced backyard backs to trees for privacy and includes two sheds, one with electricity. The double paved driveway allows for plenty of parking.Paint work Interior (Ceilings included)**Recently painted shutter**Painted Cabinets **New flooring **Shoe molding**Crown molding **Changed door knobs**Recently power washed home**Upgraded fridge **New Fire alarm**New Thermostat **Scheduled service call for AC**Upgraded bathroom exhausts fan**Changed living, dining, and hallway switches **Changed shower head **Changed registers
